Kaori!

33
00:02:49,502 --> 00:02:51,663
Kaori, hang in there, Kaori!

34
00:02:54,741 --> 00:02:59,701
Kaori Gets Amnesia!
Goodbye, My Lovely Partner

35
00:03:09,088 --> 00:03:10,112
Ryo!

36
00:03:10,823 --> 00:03:12,313
How is Kaori?

37
00:03:14,227 --> 00:03:17,390
The treatment is over. Please come in.

38
00:03:20,200 --> 00:03:21,801
Are you all right, Kaori?

39
00:03:21,801 --> 00:03:25,134
I was so surprised when I heard that you fell
down the stairs of the pedestrian overpass.

40
00:03:27,040 --> 00:03:29,838
Excuse me, but who are you people?

41
00:03:30,343 --> 00:03:31,310
Kaori...

42
00:03:34,047 --> 00:03:38,211
It seems like she has retrograde amnesia
from the brain concussion.

43
00:03:38,818 --> 00:03:40,286
Amnesia?

44
00:03:40,286 --> 00:03:45,019
Yes, but it may be a brain contusion
or encephalitis.

45
00:03:45,258 --> 00:03:50,195
I can't be certain until I see the test results.

46
00:03:54,200 --> 00:03:56,336
Will she get her memory back, Doctor?

47
00:03:56,336 --> 00:04:01,608
It might come back right away,
or it might never come back.

48
00:04:01,608 --> 00:04:05,066
There are some cases where a shock
brings the memory back suddenly.

49
00:04:09,749 --> 00:04:12,980
Please talk to the patient, about anything.

50
00:04:13,419 --> 00:04:18,152
The best way is to give her hints
about her lost memories.

51
00:04:18,558 --> 00:04:20,048
Yes!

52
00:04:32,138 --> 00:04:33,006
Hi!

53
00:04:33,006 --> 00:04:35,208
Mr. Saeba, right?

54
00:04:35,208 --> 00:04:36,776
Yes, I am.

55
00:04:36,776 --> 00:04:40,041
I feel like I've known you for a long time.

56
00:04:40,913 --> 00:04:42,676
It's been my pleasure.

57
00:04:43,049 --> 00:04:44,951
Well, do you remember me then?

58
00:04:44,951 --> 00:04:45,985
How about me?

59
00:04:45,985 --> 00:04:49,045
Well...

60
00:04:49,289 --> 00:04:50,590
Just Ryo, I guess.

61
00:04:50,590 --> 00:04:52,558
Wait, let's see...

62
00:04:52,558 --> 00:04:55,959
Don't think too hard, Kaori.
Well, I'm going to introduce myself.

63
00:04:56,229 --> 00:05:00,928
