73
00:05:31,497 --> 00:05:32,930
For Kaori only

74
00:05:34,734 --> 00:05:36,201
I'm just kidding.

75
00:05:37,103 --> 00:05:39,765
Why do I have things like this?

76
00:05:40,006 --> 00:05:42,566
It's a kind of automatic reaction.

77
00:05:42,909 --> 00:05:44,376
Reaction?

78
00:05:44,877 --> 00:05:47,675
Do I carry things like this around
with me all the time?

79
00:05:48,614 --> 00:05:50,582
I feel sorry for the person I beat with this.

80
00:05:50,983 --> 00:05:52,418
She's sorry for you.

81
00:05:52,418 --> 00:05:54,854
How impressive, I almost started crying.

82
00:05:54,854 --> 00:05:59,052
My dark days when I was living in fear
of the sneaking hammer!

83
00:06:00,026 --> 00:06:03,587
I am sorry, Mr. Saeba. I caused
you so much trouble.

84
00:06:05,298 --> 00:06:07,533
Something is different from
the way she used to be.

85
00:06:07,533 --> 00:06:10,229
I'm sure this is Kaori's real character.

86
00:06:11,204 --> 00:06:15,231
I see, she was an ordinary girl
before she knew Ryo.

87
00:06:15,675 --> 00:06:17,243
I have to be careful too.

88
00:06:17,243 --> 00:06:20,906
You, don't talk about me as if
I'm some kind of bacteria.

89
00:06:21,147 --> 00:06:22,281
It's just a joke.

90
00:06:22,281 --> 00:06:23,716
Damn!

91
00:06:23,716 --> 00:06:25,650
Ryo, where are you going?

92
00:06:26,152 --> 00:06:28,755
I'm just exploring for a white uniform
flower garden. See you.

93
00:06:28,755 --> 00:06:30,222
Ryo!

94
00:06:31,657 --> 00:06:33,522
I can't believe he's doing that at a
time like this!

95
00:06:33,693 --> 00:06:35,194
Leave him alone, Reika.

96
00:06:35,194 --> 00:06:36,329
But, Sister!

97
00:06:36,329 --> 00:06:40,925
He didn't say so, but I'm sure
he was pretty upset.

98
00:06:43,469 --> 00:06:44,937
Who is this guy? No!

99
00:06:44,937 --> 00:06:48,429
Hey, hey, mokkori with me! Why are you
running away from me?!

100
00:06:49,675 --> 00:06:51,778
How can you think he's upset?

101
00:06:51,778 --> 00:06:53,245
I take it back.

102
00:06:55,648 --> 00:06:59,812
When is your wedding ceremony?
I wonder if I can attend or not?

103
00:07:01,687 --> 00:07:06,454
Oh no, Kaori. The wedding thing
was just a joke. A lie!

104
00:07:07,093 --> 00:07:10,463
A lie? Then what kind of relationship
do you and Mr. Saeba have?

105
00:07:10,463 --> 00:07:13,626
Our relationship is not as strong as
yours and Ryo's, so don't worry.

106
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:15,668
What do you mean?

107
00:07:15,668 --> 00:07:18,604
How can I explain this to you?

108
00:07:18,604 --> 00:07:23,303
Well, you, Kaori, help with his
business, and cook for him.

109
00:07:23,709 --> 00:07:25,199
Business and meals?

110
00:07:28,581 --> 00:07:30,845
Are we married or something?

111
00:07:31,184 --> 00:07:32,752
Not yet.

112
00:07:32,752 --> 00:07:35,220
Not yet? What do you mean?

113
00:07:35,421 --> 00:07:38,356
Let's see. Well, say something!

114
00:07:38,524 --> 00:07:44,730
Right, I have to bring you your toothbrush,
towels and other stuff.

115
00:07:44,730 --> 00:07:46,632
I'm going to go to the shop downstairs.

116
00:07:46,632 --> 00:07:48,099
Reika!

117
00:07:48,868 --> 00:07:52,538
Well, I have to go to your apartment
and bring you some clothes.

118
00:07:52,538 --> 00:07:55,234
I will be right back so rest for a while.
See you later.

119
00:08:08,054 --> 00:08:09,783
What are you doing here?

120
00:08:10,523 --> 00:08:14,227
I was thinking of recruiting my new partner.

121
00:08:14,227 --> 00:08:15,595
What the hell?

122
00:08:15,595 --> 00:08:19,899
I don't want to work with a violent
woman like Kaori anymore.

123
00:08:19,899 --> 00:08:22,493
I'm going to find a gentle lady this time.

124
00:08:22,668 --> 00:08:24,470
A gentle lady!

125
00:08:24,470 --> 00:08:27,098
I see. Another idea. Can I have you
as my new partner, Reika?

126
00:08:29,075 --> 00:08:30,702
Ouch! What the hell are you doing?

127
00:08:31,177 --> 00:08:35,273
No way. How can you can say things
like that at a time like this!?

128
00:08:35,481 --> 00:08:37,717
I consider this is as a practical
problem to solve.

129
00:08:37,717 --> 00:08:41,320
