You didn't know that?

274
00:18:12,057 --> 00:18:13,524
Mr. Saeba!

275
00:18:16,395 --> 00:18:17,862
Mr. Saeba!

276
00:18:25,737 --> 00:18:27,364
What the hell is he?!

277
00:18:28,740 --> 00:18:31,176
Bastards, let Kaori go!

278
00:18:31,176 --> 00:18:32,973
Play time is over.

279
00:18:34,279 --> 00:18:37,716
What a big mouth. I'll show you play time.

280
00:18:37,716 --> 00:18:40,310
If you don't wanna lose this woman,
throw your gun towards me.

281
00:18:46,959 --> 00:18:47,755
Ouch!

282
00:18:53,732 --> 00:18:54,528
Bastard!

283
00:18:56,902 --> 00:18:57,698
Kaori!

284
00:19:07,179 --> 00:19:08,646
Kaori!

285
00:19:10,916 --> 00:19:14,283
I... I found out who I loved.

286
00:19:16,088 --> 00:19:18,716
That sweet pea, was that how you really feel?

287
00:19:19,424 --> 00:19:21,415
Is that why you had my belongings moved?

288
00:19:21,994 --> 00:19:24,121
You had better not speak now.

289
00:19:24,596 --> 00:19:29,556
Let me speak. Mr. Saeba, do you
hate me that much?

290
00:19:30,903 --> 00:19:33,872
Please, please tell me what you really think.

291
00:19:34,940 --> 00:19:36,407
I understand.

292
00:19:39,411 --> 00:19:41,845
Kaori, I...

293
00:19:49,388 --> 00:19:51,253
Kaori! Hold on!

294
00:19:52,024 --> 00:19:53,514
Kaori!

295
00:20:11,176 --> 00:20:11,972
Kaori!

296
00:20:16,215 --> 00:20:18,183
Wow, I slept so well!

297
00:20:19,952 --> 00:20:21,943
What are you all doing here?

298
00:20:22,955 --> 00:20:24,523
What is this bandage?

299
00:20:24,523 --> 00:20:27,426
I guess I fell down the stairs
of the overpass and...

300
00:20:27,426 --> 00:20:29,061
Kaori?

301
00:20:29,061 --> 00:20:30,596
Her memory must have come back.

302
00:20:30,596 --> 00:20:31,858
Yes, it's back.

303
00:20:34,333 --> 00:20:36,164
I had amnesia?

304
00:20:36,435 --> 00:20:39,063
Yes, the situation was pretty
critical at one point.

305
00:20:39,504 --> 00:20:42,905
While my memory was gone, I must have
caused you guys a lot of trouble.

306
00:20:43,208 --> 00:20:45,010
Thank you very much.

307
00:20:45,010 --> 00:20:49,881
Oh, no, don't thank us. Anyway, I'm glad
you got your memory back.

308
00:20:49,881 --> 00:20:52,907
It seems like there is one person who
is not really happy about it.

309
00:20:54,152 --> 00:20:55,454
Where is he?

310
00:20:55,454 --> 00:20:56,944
Why are you hiding, hey?!

311
00:20:57,155 --> 00:21:00,259
Well, I'm glad you're okay now, Kaori.

312
00:21:00,259 --> 00:21:04,662
You, you did something that you can't
tell me about, didn't you, Ryo?

313
00:21:10,602 --> 00:21:12,297
My stuff is gone!

314
00:21:12,738 --> 00:21:14,673
He moved it by himself.

315
00:21:14,673 --> 00:21:16,975
I said no, but he did it anyway.

316
00:21:16,975 --> 00:21:18,110
I see.

317
00:21:18,110 --> 00:21:21,705
While my memory was gone, you tried to
kick me out of here, didn't you?

318
00:21:21,980 --> 00:21:23,448
Oh, no way!

319
00:21:23,448 --> 00:21:28,317
Actually, he did. Ryo said it was a good
chance to say goodbye to you.

320
00:21:28,587 --> 00:21:29,884
Ryo!

321
00:21:30,555 --> 00:21:32,523
Please forgive me, Kaori. I'm so sorry.

322
00:21:34,126 --> 00:21:37,425
Well, I guess I forgive you this time.

323
00:21:38,630 --> 00:21:40,732
No, Kaori, you should be harder
on him than that.

324
00:21:40,732 --> 00:21:42,495
That's right! I'll support you!

325
00:21:43,235 --> 00:21:44,202
That's okay.

326
00:21:45,103 --> 00:21:47,401
I wonder if she's really got her
memory back completely?

327
00:21:48,640 --> 00:21:51,610
I had a really good dream
while I was sleeping.

328
00:21:51,610 --> 00:21:53,077
Good dream?

329
00:21:53,578 --> 00:21:55,045
Ryo told me...

330
00:21:55,180 --> 00:21:56,909
He told you what?

331
00:21:58,016 --> 00:21:59,142
It's a secret.

332
00:22:00,619 --> 00:22:03,520
She can dream whatever she wants to.

333
00:22:04,856 --> 00:22:06,050
He says dream.

334
00:22:09,194 --> 00:22:12,459
It might be a good thing to get amnesia.

335
00:22:13,131 --> 00:22:14,689
Me too.

